<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 12:11:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>被首相苏纳克停职的英国议员加入右翼英国改革党</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-lawmaker-suspended-by-pm-sunak-joins-right-wing-reform-uk-party/articleshow/108395200.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108395200.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;前保守党副主席李·安德森叛逃至右翼改革英国党，威胁到首相里希·苏纳克的连任竞选。安德森支持死刑和严格的移民法，并批评伦敦的穆斯林市长。此举是在以色列与哈马斯战争和移民立法造成紧张局势之际做出的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 10:57:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-lawmaker-suspended-by-pm-sunak-joins-right-wing-reform-uk-party/articleshow/108395200.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国通过法律赋予共产党更多对内阁的控制权</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-passes-law-granting-communist-party-more-control-over-cabinet/articleshow/108394087.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108394087.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国人大已批准修改一项法律，赋予共产党对国家内阁国务院的更多控制权。此举是在总理的议会后新闻发布会30年来首次被取消之后做出的。修改后的国务院组织法在北京举行的全国人民代表大会上以过半数代表获得通过。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 10:32:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-passes-law-granting-communist-party-more-control-over-cabinet/articleshow/108394087.cms</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫拒绝对美国准备俄罗斯对乌克兰进行核打击的报告发表评论</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/kremlin-declines-comment-on-report-us-prepared-for-russian-nuclear-strike-in-ukraine/articleshow/108391881.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108391881.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;克里姆林宫周一拒绝对 CNN 的一篇报道发表评论，该报道称，美国在 2022 年底开始为俄罗斯可能用核武器袭击乌克兰做好严格准备。美国有线电视新闻网周六报道称，美国总统乔·拜登的政府特别担心俄罗斯可能在乌克兰使用战术或战场核武器。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 09:31:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/kremlin-declines-comment-on-report-us-prepared-for-russian-nuclear-strike-in-ukraine/articleshow/108391881.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜副外相罕见访问蒙古</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-koreas-vice-foreign-minister-in-mongolia-on-rare-visit/articleshow/108391725.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108391725.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;朴明浩在蒙古国与外长阿马图夫辛·贡博苏伦举行会谈。这次访问正值平壤在疫情期间关闭边境后似乎开始扩大外交接触之际。双方讨论了两国友好关系的稳步发展，同意采取实际行动措施恢复各领域合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 09:40:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-koreas-vice-foreign-minister-in-mongolia-on-rare-visit/articleshow/108391725.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国通过法律赋予共产党更多对内阁的控制权</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-passes-law-granting-communist-party-more-control-over-cabinet/articleshow/108389656.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108389656.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;国务院组织法的修改深化了党对国家机关和党国体制的控制。它设立新的委员会并侵犯经济和金融政策。总理取消新闻发布会是党加强控制的另一个例子。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 08:28:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-passes-law-granting-communist-party-more-control-over-cabinet/articleshow/108389656.cms</guid></item><item><title>“除了普京之外谁都可以”：塞尔维亚的俄罗斯人投票没有希望</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/anybody-but-putin-russians-in-serbia-vote-without-hope/articleshow/108388342.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108388342.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 07:55:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/anybody-but-putin-russians-in-serbia-vote-without-hope/articleshow/108388342.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国发现5人死亡 警方怀疑他杀自杀</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/5-people-found-dead-in-us-police-suspect-murder-suicide/articleshow/108387765.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108387765.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;夏威夷檀香山市有五人被发现死亡，其中包括三名儿童，这起案件似乎是一起谋杀自杀案。警方认为丈夫刺伤了妻子和孩子。一个匿名电话报警了。这起事件是该州自 1999 年施乐谋杀案以来最严重的大规模凶杀案。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 07:39:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/5-people-found-dead-in-us-police-suspect-murder-suicide/articleshow/108387765.cms</guid></item><item><title>关于俄罗斯总统选举你需要了解的五件事</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/five-things-to-know-about-russias-presidential-vote/articleshow/108385257.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108385257.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯将于周五至周日举行总统选举，尽管俄罗斯在乌克兰的竞选活动引发了骚乱，但总统弗拉基米尔·普京将再次获得六年任期。他们都支持俄罗斯对乌克兰的进攻。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 06:22:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/five-things-to-know-about-russias-presidential-vote/articleshow/108385257.cms</guid></item><item><title>精疲力尽、储备减少和指挥官失踪：乌克兰如何将阿夫季夫卡输给俄罗斯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/exhaustion-dwindling-reserves-and-a-commander-who-disappeared-how-ukraine-lost-avdiivka-to-russia/articleshow/108383428.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108383428.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于弹药不足、俄罗斯的攻击势不可挡以及军事管理不善，乌克兰在阿夫迪夫卡战役中遭受重大失败。士兵们感到被他们的最高指挥部和西方盟友抛弃了。俄罗斯人占领了焦化厂并声称控制了阿夫季夫卡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 05:24:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/exhaustion-dwindling-reserves-and-a-commander-who-disappeared-how-ukraine-lost-avdiivka-to-russia/articleshow/108383428.cms</guid></item><item><title>大选前的俄罗斯电视台只有一个节目：普京的节目</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/on-russian-tv-ahead-of-the-election-theres-only-one-program-putins/articleshow/108383382.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108383382.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由克里姆林宫控制的俄罗斯国家电视台忽视了反抗普京的事件，而专注于宣传以支撑人们的精神。独立媒体已被消灭，大多数俄罗斯人只能依赖国家电视台。宣传民族主义主题是为了鼓励选举中的高投票率。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 05:23:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/on-russian-tv-ahead-of-the-election-theres-only-one-program-putins/articleshow/108383382.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京：独裁者着眼于新的世界秩序</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-the-autocrat-eyeing-a-new-world-order/articleshow/108385103.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108385103.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 06:19:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-the-autocrat-eyeing-a-new-world-order/articleshow/108385103.cms</guid></item><item><title>五名越野滑雪运动员在瑞士被发现死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/five-cross-country-skiers-found-dead-in-switzerland/articleshow/108382855.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108382855.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;五名越野滑雪运动员在瑞士瓦莱州被发现死亡。第六名滑雪者在从采尔马特出发的滑雪之旅中失踪，目前仍在搜寻中。滑雪者在采尔马特-阿罗拉路径上的太特布兰奇山附近失踪。风暴和雪崩使直升机和救援人员无法接近该地区。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 05:06:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/five-cross-country-skiers-found-dead-in-switzerland/articleshow/108382855.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳航调整时间表，机组飞行员计划再次罢工</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/qantas-adjusting-schedule-as-pilots-at-units-plan-another-strike/articleshow/108382869.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108382869.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚旗舰航空公司澳洲航空 (Qantas Airways) 周一表示，将调整本周几天的航班时刻表，以减轻因飞行员新计划罢工而造成的运营中断。该航空公司预计，大多数乘客将在预订当天搭乘澳洲航空自有飞机和第三方飞机抵达目的地。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 05:07:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/qantas-adjusting-schedule-as-pilots-at-units-plan-another-strike/articleshow/108382869.cms</guid></item><item><title>吉娜·雷蒙多：美国的目标是成为印太地区的“首选经济伙伴”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-aims-to-be-economic-partner-of-choice-for-indo-pacific-gina-raimondo/articleshow/108382032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108382032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国商务部长吉娜·雷蒙多率领贸易代表团访问菲律宾和泰国，以加强经济联系、促进区域供应链并对抗中国的侵略行为。该代表团包括来自美国联合航空公司、谷歌、Visa、联邦快递和微软的高管。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 04:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-aims-to-be-economic-partner-of-choice-for-indo-pacific-gina-raimondo/articleshow/108382032.cms</guid></item><item><title>克服以色列的限制，许多巴勒斯坦人发现很难到达阿克萨清真寺</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/navigating-israeli-restrictions-many-palestinians-find-it-hard-to-reach-al-aqsa/articleshow/108381562.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108381562.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;每周五，13 岁的 Yousef al-Sideeq 都会被以色列警方阻止进入阿克萨清真寺。穆斯林进入清真寺受到越来越多的限制，引发了人们对斋月期间礼拜自由受到限制的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 04:18:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/navigating-israeli-restrictions-many-palestinians-find-it-hard-to-reach-al-aqsa/articleshow/108381562.cms</guid></item><item><title>俾路支省首席部长宣布对分离主义者进行“大赦”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/balochistan-cm-announces-general-amnesty-for-separatists/articleshow/108381351.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108381351.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据《新闻国际》报道，俾路支省首席部长萨弗拉兹·布格蒂敦促俾路支叛乱分子停止暴力并加入主流政治，并补充说巴基斯坦人民党（PPP）领导的政府将宣布“大赦”，通过对话解决问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 04:10:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/balochistan-cm-announces-general-amnesty-for-separatists/articleshow/108381351.cms</guid></item><item><title>基地组织也门分支称领导人哈立德·巴塔菲死因不明</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/al-qaidas-yemen-branch-says-leader-khalid-al-batarfi-dead-in-unclear-circumstances/articleshow/108380035.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108380035.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;也门基地组织领导人哈立德·巴塔尔菲 (Khalid al-Batarfi) 已死亡。萨阿德·本·阿特夫·奥拉基 (Saad bin Atef al-Awlaki) 成为新领导人。基地组织声称对 2015 年查理周刊袭击事件负责。前领导人卡西姆·里米被美国无人机袭击身亡。巴塔菲曾在阿富汗作战，并在也门阿比扬省领导部队。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:22:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/al-qaidas-yemen-branch-says-leader-khalid-al-batarfi-dead-in-unclear-circumstances/articleshow/108380035.cms</guid></item><item><title>加勒比紧急峰会解决海地黑帮危机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/emergency-caribbean-summit-to-address-haiti-gang-crisis/articleshow/108378782.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108378782.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;来自主要国家的特使将于周一在加勒比地区举行会议，讨论海地不断升级的局势，因为帮派暴力使这个贫穷的岛国首都陷入瘫痪，并迫使外国外交官在周末逃离。加勒比国家联盟加共体已召集美国、法国、加拿大和联合国的特使在牙买加举行会议，讨论暴力事件以及向海地提供援助的方式。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 02:30:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/emergency-caribbean-summit-to-address-haiti-gang-crisis/articleshow/108378782.cms</guid></item><item><title>新闻机构召回英国王妃凯特·米德尔顿的术后照片</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/news-agencies-recall-post-surgery-image-of-uks-princess-kate-middleton-over-manipulation/articleshow/108378075.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108378075.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于担心潜在的数字操纵，许多知名新闻媒体撤回了肯辛顿宫发布的一张威尔士王妃凯瑟琳和她的孩子们的照片。包括路透社、美联社、盖蒂和法新社在内的照片发行商都撤回了肯辛顿宫上周日分发的母亲节图片，理由是怀疑存在数字篡改。这张照片展示了凯特·米德尔顿和她的三个孩子。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 01:39:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/news-agencies-recall-post-surgery-image-of-uks-princess-kate-middleton-over-manipulation/articleshow/108378075.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人在加沙战争的阴影下准备斋月</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-prepare-for-ramadan-in-the-shadow-of-gaza-war/articleshow/108373865.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108373865.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 19:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-prepare-for-ramadan-in-the-shadow-of-gaza-war/articleshow/108373865.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>